trailingComments.value:
*
 * Adds additional graph features to the graph such as mixed attributes or 
 * distractor graphs. If they don't exist, plot_graph function is called
 * normally.
 * 
 * @param {object} chart - d3 chart
 * @param {assoc. array} graph_attributes - target graph properties and dataset
 * @param {assoc. array} distractor_attributes - distractor graph properties and dataset
 * @param {function} x_data_scale - x axis scale function
 * @param {function} y_data_scale -y axis scale function
 * @param {function} plot_graph - graph plotting function
